# Unlike the original repo's .dockerignore, .git IS excluded here — this repo's
# Dockerfile is for the Kubernetes deployment, and a production image has no
# use for git history (only makes the image larger and copies commit metadata
# unnecessarily). If this repo genuinely needs that carried over, re-add a
# "!.git" style exception rather than removing this comment.
.git
